title: 662. Reacting to the 49ers, Dolphins, and Eagles Draft Pick Trades
itunes:title: 662. Reacting to the 49ers, Dolphins, and Eagles Draft Pick Trades
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks! First, DJ and Bucky react to recent the trade with the Miami Dolphins moving the San Francisco 49ers up from the 12th draft position to the 3rd position and if Alabama QB Mac Jones could be the pick at that slot (0:33). Then, the hosts discuss the Dolphins next move, trading with the Philadelphia Eagles to move from the 12th draft position to the 6th. First they evaluate the trade from the Dolphins perspective (20:13), and then from the Eagles perspective (26:50). After that, the guys discuss DJ's top 50 prospects 3.0 and which cornerbacks will be most coveted in this year's draft (30:38). Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
